OL,3,CCopper could be mined on Anglesey again
OL,5,FThere could be a gold rush on Anglesey
OL,6,F- well, copper rush, to be more
OL,7,Faccurate.
OL,9,FPlans have been announced to restart
OL,10,Funcovering precious metals at Parys
OL,11,FMountain, just south of Amlwch.
OL,13,FIt has been 120 years since the last
OL,14,Fminers left, but its history goes back
OL,15,Feven further.
OL,17,F"It actually goes back to the bronze
OL,18,Fage, there's traces of bronze age
OL,19,Fmining here," said Don McCallum, site
OL,20,Fmanager.
