OL,3,CCopper could be mined on Anglesey again
OL,5,FHe says there is plenty more material
OL,6,Fleft available in the mine, due to
OL,7,Fdevelopments in techniques since the
OL,8,F1900s.
OL,10,F"The techniques that they used then
OL,11,Fwere limited, it was all done by hand
OL,12,For by horse or by sticks of dynamite,"
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,FAnglesey Mining hope that over a
OL,16,Fdecade or so, a billion pounds' worth
OL,17,Fof copper, gold, and silver, along
OL,18,Fwith other metals, could be mined at
OL,19,Fthe site.
