OL,3,CCopper could be mined on Anglesey again
OL,5,FRob Marsden, chief executive of
OL,6,FAnglesey Mining, said the mine also
OL,7,Fcontained deposits of silver and lead.
OL,9,FHe said: "Parys Mountain is
OL,10,Fdemonstrably the largest and most
OL,11,Fadvanced project for mining copper,
OL,12,Fgold, silver, lead and zinc in the UK.
OL,14,F"The project is favourably located on
OL,15,Fa previously permitted development
OL,16,Fsite with significant existing
OL,17,Finfrastructure already in place."
