OL,3,CCopper could be mined on Anglesey again
OL,5,FBefore that can begin, though, it'll
OL,6,Fhave to pass a number of surveys to
OL,7,Fcheck local wildlife like bats, birds
OL,8,Fand plants.
OL,10,FIf the project is approved, it would
OL,11,Fbe the UK's only domestic source of
OL,12,Fcopper. The country uses around 15,000
OL,13,Ftonnes a year, all of which is
OL,14,Fcurrently imported.
